summary: I am a creative, artistic and ambitious Graphics Designer and Programmer with a longing desire to design which stems from my affinity for order and geometry. Due to my attention for detail, I am constantly absorbing ideas from everyday life. Currently I study ICT, Application and Media Development. I am passionate about the work I can do to satisfy clients and seeing the positive impact, I create for people's lives and business.
